{"tid":753007,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：美國在貿易問題上威脅中國是無用的","createTime":"2018-07-23T09:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T01:44:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1439e8dac880c7cf20a6d04aeef8884305e0d637","tid":753007,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普早前接受美國電視台CNBC訪問時指，已準備好對全數約5050億美元的中國進口商品加徵關稅。中國外交部則稱，美國在貿易問題上對中國的威脅和恫嚇是沒有用的。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人耿爽表示，希望美國以冷靜、合理的方式處理貿易問題。對於近期人民幣走弱，美國財長梅努欽曾對中國發出警告，並稱會關注人民幣動向，以尋找是否存在操控的跡象。耿爽回應指，中方沒必要通過貨幣競爭性貶值來支持出口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180723/s00002/1532334848072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180723%2Fs00002%2F1532334848072&d=ZxeHy217KvZL1YY2zO4x2UzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=e9198ca6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180723%2Fs00002%2F1532334848072&h=1ad1c504\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180723/s00002/1532334848072</a>"},{"pid":"1b1fb85cab52697e8c0e1b4ab6e9dc004188a7a2","tid":753007,"uid":14918,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:19:30.000Z","msg":"外交部話無用即係有用<br />\n<br />\n空即是色 色即是空<br />\n空即是色 色即是空"},{"pid":"bf1925cbcdfe8c984d3ff4ff12e8df66aef6bc6f","tid":753007,"uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:22:07.000Z","msg":"耿爽表示，對於美方執意挑起貿易戰，中方「不願打、不怕打、必要時不得不打」的立場非常堅定、明確；<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第一，中國不是嚇大的</span>，中方有能力、有信心維護中國人民的利益。第二，<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我們奉勸美方保持冷靜，通過理性的態度來處理和解決有關問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2121187/%E4%BA%AC%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9D%9E%E5%9A%87%E5%A4%A7%20%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%A8%81%E9%80%BC%E7%84%A1%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u